  "body": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\"><strong><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Variant_Chiseled_Bookshelves/BH_Variant_Chiseled_Bookshelves_Header.webp\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">Unlock the secrets of ancient knowledge and elevate your library aesthetics with the 'Variant Chiseled Bookshelves' mod. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">This enchanting addition to Minecraft introduces a range of elegant bookshelves, each designed to complement the game's classic wood styles. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">Immerse yourself in the rich textures and hues of oak, birch, spruce, jungle, acacia, dark oak, crimson, bamboo, mangrove, cherry and warped bookshelves. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">Whether you're expanding your enchanting room or creating a cozy reading nook, 'Variant Chiseled Bookshelves' offers both functionality and aesthetics. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">Discover the beauty of customised book storage with this captivating mod!</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6UHsUm3.png\" /></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">Variant Chiseled Bookshelves adds a new Chiseled Bookshelf for each vanilla Plank type.</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">All textures have been compressed (without any negative impact) to keep the mod file size to an absolute minimum.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">All textures are manually created using the hex colours from the appropriate planks to ensure they look correct.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">Un-crafting for all variants back to vanilla has been included in case of any issues.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">Vanilla bookshelf renamed to Oak and recoloured slightly to better fit the Oak wood type.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h6><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6UHsUm3.png\" /></span></h6>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\" border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://discord.gg/JMxYXtMz5r\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Discord&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=452161&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"208\" height=\"50\" /></a></span></td>\n<td><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/xanthian\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Github&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=452161&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"200\" height=\"50\" /></a></span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/xanthian\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Variant_Crafting/BH_VC_BisectPromo.png\" width=\"533\" height=\"80\" /></a></p>",
